TY  - JOUR
T1  - Dynamic Capabilities and the Role of Managers in Business Strategy and Economic Performance
AU  - Augier, Mie
AU  - Teece, David J.
Y1  - 2009/04/01
PY  - 2009
DA  - 2009/04/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/orsc.1090.0424
DO  - 10.1287/orsc.1090.0424
T2  - Organization Science
